{"tid":2451796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6.12中彈老吳涉旺角拒捕開審 警稱被告全身放軟雙手放胸前避上手銬","createTime":"2021-03-18T10:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T14:10:57.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"895ea087aeea46d674cb5f9ecc0e243dcfdde391","tid":2451796,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"前年6.12在金鐘腹部中彈的退休漢「老吳」吳應武，被指去年1月在旺角坐在行人路上不願離開並掙扎，被控一項抗拒警務人員罪。案件今在西九龍法院開審，當日拘捕被告的警員供稱，警告被告3次他都不願離開，故以非法集結罪將他拘捕，但被告卻將手放在心口、使警員難以將他雙手鎖上手扣，期後被告又放軟全身，不願意被押上警車。<br />\n<br />\n表被告的資深大律師潘熙庭上透露，<span class=\"red\">被告早前曾患骨癌及羊癇症；前年則患肺癌及哮喘</span>，需定時服用多種藥物，或需較長時間休息。<br />\n<br />\n警員22266梁國華稱當時<span class=\"red\">需用力將他的手屈到背後上手銬</span>，其間被告腳曾經向後踢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sQhQe5oz5WDcencgZBXOIpiIgq8=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5AI356LMIVCMJF7ADEA7X5MA6M.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsQhQe5oz5WDcencgZBXOIpiIgq8%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5AI356LMIVCMJF7ADEA7X5MA6M.JPG&h=117001a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁承認自己為事件錄取三份口供，第三份口供在案發10個月後錄取，他稱收到通知刑事偵緝警員要求，將案發時「拘捕過程寫得詳細少少」後錄取。<span class=\"red\">梁亦同意第三份口供部份內容在記事冊及第一份口供並沒有提及過。</span>"},{"pid":"98225b418638206f9bc7a9a956296404d9bd9f64","tid":2451796,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/M5FXMQAZSBEPPGXSGVFCESPMEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FM5FXMQAZSBEPPGXSGVFCESPMEU%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2UaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=589c0bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FM5FXMQAZSBEPPGXSGVFCESPMEU%2F&h=6bb7b516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/M5FXMQAZSBEPPGXSGVFCESPMEU/</a>"},{"pid":"37af623ccd23446c9555940dc7dd9512a8517ddb","tid":2451796,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3e744d979f2d88e52e0201443beda513687224","tid":2451796,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061bbfdc38f219a0c064ca5147f1c5d377fa519b","tid":2451796,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbf7782856b7dd4a7e63dd07ea7f85f842fc4de7","tid":2451796,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"梁為被告鎖上塑膠手扣時，被告揮動雙手掙扎，並將雙手收到胸前，期間不時大聲辱罵警員。梁於是嘗試將被告雙手抽出來，被告則用腳向後踢，警長 51624 見狀上前控制被告雙腿，令梁成功鎖上手扣。<br />\n<br />\n梁指，被告遭制服後依舊表現不合作，在他與警長將被告抬上警車時，被告故意放軟身體，不願配合警方行動。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/1-19-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E6%82%A3%E7%99%8C%E6%BC%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E6%8F%AE%E6%89%8B%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E/?fbclid=IwAR0SFtySgeY1JMp1uUWabKwhcsZR88fMw-jtoLFgbMzDzJXq5ZvQCAnNpG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F1-19-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%2599%258C%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%258F%25AE%25E6%2